{"Title":"杏仁茶的做法","Primary":["德芙原粒什锦巧克力20g","糯米10g"],"Auxiliary":["元贞糖适量"],"Flavoring":[],"Setups":["1.糯米洗净","[image]:http://images.meishij.net/p/20120327/4597e4d48ba5272beb3105b9089bc7d3.jpg","2.清水浸泡3——4小时","[image]:http://images.meishij.net/p/20120327/a49345882cd28bc3ee87b7c8379a71de.jpg","3.杏仁用开水浸泡10分钟左右","[image]:http://images.meishij.net/p/20120327/63775b6196e8d5cd1a5dd83684e3b72c.jpg","4.将杏仁去皮洗净","[image]:http://images.meishij.net/p/20120327/e9a7b4b60ab42786acb942b79cfa3fdc.jpg","5.将泡好的糯米连水倒入豆浆机中","[image]:http://images.meishij.net/p/20120327/4438a7a1757eb835a99406717a49dc68.jpg","6.将洗净的杏仁倒入豆浆机中","[image]:http://images.meishij.net/p/20120327/f89388f9a7f576d24b265838e850e8e5.jpg","7.加水至上下刻度线之间","[image]:http://images.meishij.net/p/20120327/beff7e2e7b1bec1a3666b38f4d2d0976.jpg","8.连接电源线","[image]:http://images.meishij.net/p/20120327/8d25d1b743b53bef7bf281fd0c3381e0.jpg","9.选取五谷豆浆键","[image]:http://images.meishij.net/p/20120327/17fe807bd4dc522cb3fa4cde6fa3a567.jpg","10.待蜂鸣声响起，拔掉电源线","[image]:http://images.meishij.net/p/20120327/b4b0219ea15753dbe91b46b12c7bffa6.jpg","11.打好的杏仁茶","[image]:http://images.meishij.net/p/20120327/f14b73ab848106c1cee2ad2281c06c4b.jpg","12.倒入碗中，喜欢细腻口感的可过滤一下，但其实真没什么渣，我没有过滤","[image]:http://images.meishij.net/p/20120327/5a1f02c0adc95c6d9fa3bc1d108a8065.jpg","13.依个人口味，加适量糖调味","[image]:http://images.meishij.net/p/20120327/208150e62e0966048549f26111dc32df.jpg"]}